most of the solved by bfs , dfs

kab kya use karna h?



2️⃣ DFS (Depth-First Search)

Idea: ek path me jitna ho sake deep jao, phir backtrack karo.

Use stack (recursion automatically stack use karta hai).

Use cases

Find connected components

Detect cycles in graph

Topological sort (DAG)

Maze solving (go deep first)

Easy analogy:

Ek cave me ghus rahe ho → jitna andar ja sakte ho jao, wapas aa kar dusra path try karo.

3️⃣ BFS (Breadth-First Search)

Idea: ek level pe saare neighbors visit karo, phir next level.

Use queue.

Use cases

Shortest path in unweighted graph

Level order traversal

Connected components (similar to DFS)

Minimum steps problems

Easy analogy:

Tumhara friend ek party me hai, sab first floor ke log milne jao, phir second floor, phir third → level by level.


